fields.description: Insurance Australia Group Limited is a multinational insurance company headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
Microsoft Corporation is an American multinational technology company with headquarters in Redmond, Washington.
Macquarie Group Limited is a global diversified financial group. Headquartered in Sydney, Macquarie is the world's largest infrastructure asset manager.
Atlassian Corporation Plc is an Australian enterprise software company headquartered in Sydney and founded by UNSW alumni, Mike Cannon-Brookes and Scott Farquhar.
PricewaterhouseCoopers is a multinational professional services network headquartered in London, UK. It is the second largest professional services firm in the world.
Commonwealth Bank is Australia’s leading provider of integrated financial services, including retail, premium, business and institutional banking and funds management.
UNSW Business School is one of the leading business school's in Australia with state of the art facilities and is ranked amongst the top 50 Business School's worldwide!
